Class CefZipArchive::File

CefBase
   |
   +--CefZipArchive::File
   in cef_zip_archive.h
class CefZipArchive::File
extends CefBase

Class representing a file in the archive. Accessing the file data from multiple threads is safe provided a reference to the File object is kept.

Method Summary
